<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://apelbaum.wordpress.com/2009/03/" class="external text" title="http://apelbaum.wordpress.com/2009/03/" rel="nofollow">"An Afternoon with a Fraudster"</a>. Apelbaum. 2009<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://apelbaum.wordpress.com/2009/03/" class="external free" title="http://apelbaum.wordpress.com/2009/03/" rel="nofollow">http://apelbaum.wordpress.com/2009/03/</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=An+Afternoon+with+a+Fraudster&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft.pub=Apelbaum&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fapelbaum.wordpress.com%2F2009%2F03%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Credit_card_fraud"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
