<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Credit_card_fraud&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<p><a name="Reporting_credit_card_fraud_over_the_Internet" id="Reporting_credit_card_fraud_over_the_Internet"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Credit_card_fraud&amp;action=edit&amp;section=23" title="Edit section: Reporting credit card fraud over the Internet">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Reporting credit card fraud over the Internet</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.ic3.gov" class="external text" title="http://www.ic3.gov" rel="nofollow">The Internet Crime Complaint Center (IC3)</a> is a partnership between the Federal Bureau of Investigation (FBI) and the National White Collar Crime Center (NW3C).</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="General_fraud_information" id="General_fraud_information"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Credit_card_fraud&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Edit section: General fraud information">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">General fraud information</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.apacs.org.uk" class="external text" title="http://www.apacs.org.uk" rel="nofollow">cheque and card fraud information from APACS</a> The UK Payments Association monitors online and card fraud in the UK.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ftc.gov/sentinel/" class="external text" title="http://www.ftc.gov/sentinel/" rel="nofollow">Consumer Sentinel</a> Fraud tips, reporting, trends and other general information.</li>
</ul>


